REACTION   (22-TI-48(P,INL)22-TI-48,PAR,DA,,REL)
           No explanation of relative units is given.
SAMPLE     (22-TI-48,ENR=0.987) Targets were prepared by
           evaporation of Ti-48 onto thin (15-20 ug/cm2) self-
           supporting carbon films. The number of Ti atoms was
           5*10**17 atoms/cm2. Energy losses in target were
           3.1 keV.
